PointToLineDistance:

求直线line外的一点p到直线的距离：
  line:o(线上的任意一点), dir(单位向量)
  p:p
  用点积来计算
    calByDot: vector3 op = p - o;
              float proj = Vector3.Dot(op, dir);
              vector3 oe = o + dir * proj;
              vector3 pe = oe - op;
              return pe.magnitude;
    calByCross: vector3 op = p - o;
                vector3 cross = Vector3.cross(op, dir);
                return cross.magnitude;
